## Quick Context (for any Claude session)

**What is this?**
- React 18 + Vite + Tailwind MVP for yoga/wellness travel company
- ✅ All 6 pages built and deployed
- ✅ Form email integration working (Simple Forms API)
- ✅ Design system complete (Tailwind tokens)

**Tech Stack**
- Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + Vite
- Form Validation: Zod + react-hook-form
- Form Email: Simple Forms API (staticforms.dev)
- Deployment: Vercel (auto-deploy from GitHub main branch)
- Status: ✅ MVP COMPLETE, live at https://yoga-journey.vercel.app/

**Project Status: MVP COMPLETE ✅**
- Built: 6/6 pages (100%)
- Features: Form email, SPA routing, dynamic pages, validation
- Design System: 100% (all tokens in Tailwind config)
