5. ✅ Privacy - Full 14-section legal privacy policy
6. ✅ Layout - Header and Footer with navigation

**Features Implemented**
- ✅ Form validation (Zod + react-hook-form)
- ✅ Responsive design (mobile-first Tailwind)
