**Tech Decisions Made**
- Vite instead of Next.js (faster, lighter, suitable for MVP)
- Simple Forms API instead of custom backend (free, reliable, no infrastructure needed)
- Client-side SPA routing instead of Next.js pages (simpler, works on Vercel)
- Tailwind CSS for design system (fast, maintainable, design tokens in config)

